==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fusiform
<hw>Fu"si*form</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fusus</ets> spindle + <ets>-form</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>fusiforme</ets>.]</ety> <def>Shaped like a spindle; shaped like a
cylinder that tapers at each end; <as>as, a <ex>fusiform</ex> root; a
<ex>fusiform</ex> cell.</as></def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> cigar-shaped.</syn>
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

